{"tid":2261480,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子到中區警署聲援鍾翰林 叫港獨口號涉黨安法被捕","createTime":"2020-10-28T10:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T11:28:29.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a93c898bb0ea0256dc27fbb5d522651706cebb8b","tid":2261480,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"男子到中區警署聲援鍾翰林 叫港獨口號被捕<br />\n<br />\n兩名男子傍晚到上環中區警署外，聲援涉違反港區國安法被捕的前學生動源召集人鍾翰林。其中一人舉港獨標語及高叫口號，其後被幾名警員用橙帶包圍截查，然後帶走。另一名男子只高舉報章，被截查後獲放行。<br />\n<br />\n警方國家安全處昨日拘捕鍾翰林等3人，涉嫌煽動他人分裂國家。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2363661\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2363661&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7FcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=a43137ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2363661</a>"},{"pid":"663e6d1d889b85539f61b7d73c7a808dcfafb112","tid":2261480,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"又係美國隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d3ac118ad7db7bb42e50d72e0cecf939ebd6d0","tid":2261480,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfbddc75b039aff94ac3ee507340039996a8de6","tid":2261480,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:24:41.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccbd06aaad0cb1ed27ac08bd97e8c73a3ff66bc","tid":2261480,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"嗌口號咁勇武 我地和理非課光時算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}